txt.en: There is much to be done in the Towers of the Teeth.

Enter the Towers of the Teeth
On your return delve beneath Carchost, you notice the Enemy are gathered in encampments. It would be easy to sow mayhem by torching those camps.
The Towers of the Teeth are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should destroy camp-tents in the Towers of the Teeth.
The Towers of the Teeth are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should destroy camp-tents in the Towers of the Teeth.
You have destroyed many of the encampments within the Towers of the Teeth. Your efforts will surely affect the Enemy gathered here.
Destroyed many tents in the Towers of the Teeth.
